snippet.title: Awesome - Amiga Game (1/9) Aquoss
snippet.description:
A playthrough of the 1st planet, Aquoss.

It's possible to return to Aquoss, theres even a contract available at Tundrars that takes you back here, however it will jump you straight into the first fight without giving you a chance to choose your equipment.
